<bibRefCitation author="Smit, J. T. &amp; van Harten, A. &amp; Ketelaar, R." box="[721,903,1871,1898]" pageId="54" pageNumber="55" refId="ref40237" refString="Smit, J. T., van Harten, A. &amp; Ketelaar, R. (2017) Order Diptera, family Syrphidae the hoverflies of the Arabian Peninsula. In: van Harten, A. (Eds.), Arthropod fauna of the UAE. Vol. 6. Department of the President's Affairs, Abu Dhabi, pp. 572 - 612." type="book" year="2017">
